column1: The NTC R/T Calculator tool may be used to determine certain capabilities of Vishay NTC thermistors.
Utilizing data provided by the user, the tool can generate standard R/T tables for such thermistors. The
NTC R/T Calculator tool is provided solely on an "AS IS" and "AS AVAILABLE" basis for the convenience
